org.hkijena.jipipe.api.parameters

Class DefaultJIPipeParameterGenerator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hkijena.jipipe.api.parameters.DefaultJIPipeParameterGenerator
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    JIPipeValidatable, JIPipeParameterCollection, JIPipeParameterGenerator
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    EnumParameterGenerator, NumberRangeParameterGenerator

    public abstract class DefaultJIPipeParameterGenerator
extends Object
implements JIPipeParameterGenerator, JIPipeParameterCollection, JIPipeValidatable
    A default implementation of JIPipeParameterGenerator that shows all parameters of this JIPipeParameterCollection in a dialog before generating the data. The dialog input is checked by the validation function.
